\v 16 ‚Äå ªOku foaki mai  ªae Tohitapu kotoa pƒì  ªi he fakamƒÅnava  ªae  ªOtua, pea  ªoku  ªaonga ia ki he akonaki, mo e valoki, mo e fakatonutonu, mo e fakapoto ki he mƒÅ ªoni ªoni:  
